                    <history>
                        <origin>
                            <origDate notBefore="1800" notAfter="1950">19th–mid-20th century.</origDate>
                        </origin>
                        <provenance>
                            At one point, the manuscript belonged to <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14687GabraYohannes">Gabra Yoḥannəs</persName>,
                            whose name is included in the supplication at the end of <ref target="#a3"/>.
                            At some point in the 1950s, it was sent by its then owner <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8215Rosen">Björn von Rosen</persName>
                            to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6337Lofgren">Oscar Anders Valfrid Löfgren</persName> in order to be catalogued (see 
                            <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/X4SBAXAT"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><title level="m">Katalog über die äthiopischen Handschriften in der Universitätsbibliothek Uppsala, Sowie Anhänge über äthiopische Handschriften in anderen Bibliotheken und in Privatbesitz in Schweden</title><title level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Oscar</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Löfgren</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Uppsala</pubPlace><publisher>Almqvist &amp; Wiksell</publisher><date>1974</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">18</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">8</citedRange></bibl>).
                            Presumably, it was still in the possession of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8215Rosen">Björn von Rosen</persName> in
                            <date when="1974"/>, as this is the information provided in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/X4SBAXAT"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><title level="m">Katalog über die äthiopischen Handschriften in der Universitätsbibliothek Uppsala, Sowie Anhänge über äthiopische Handschriften in anderen Bibliotheken und in Privatbesitz in Schweden</title><title level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Oscar</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Löfgren</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Uppsala</pubPlace><publisher>Almqvist &amp; Wiksell</publisher><date>1974</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">18</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope></bibl>.
                        </provenance>
                        <acquisition>According to <ref target="#e4"/>, the manuscript reached its current repository
                            in <date when="1979"/>.</acquisition>
                    </history>

